 tag deactivation, the tag must be currently active and manually defined.\";'),(_binary 'en',_binary 'messages:apihelp-managetags-param-tags',_binary 's:60:\"Change tags to apply to the entry in the tag management log.\";'),(_binary 'en',_binary 'messages:apihelp-managetags-summary',_binary 's:49:\"Perform management tasks relating to change tags.\";'),(_binary 'en',_binary 'messages:apihelp-mergehistory-example-merge',_binary 's:71:\"Merge the entire history of <kbd>Oldpage</kbd> into <kbd>Newpage</kbd>.\";'),(_binary 'en',_binary 'messages:apihelp-mergehistory-example-merge-timestamp',_binary 's:116:\"Merge the page revisions of <kbd>Oldpage</kbd> dating up to <kbd>2015-12-31T04:37:41Z</kbd> into <kbd>Newpage</kbd>.\";'),(_binary 'en',_binary 'messages:apihelp-mergehistory-param-from',_binary 's:102:\"Title of the page from which history will be merged. Cannot be used together with <var>$1fromid</var>.\";'),(_binary 'en',_binary 'messages:apihelp-mergehistory-param-fromid',_binary 's:102:\"Page ID of the page from which history will be merged. Cannot be used together with <var>$1from</var>.\";'),(_binary 'en',_binary 'messages:apihelp-mergehistory-param-reason',_binary 's:29:\"Reason for the history merge.\";'),(_binary 'en',_binary 'messages:apihelp-mergehistory-param-timestamp',_binary 's:208:\"Timestamp up to which revisions will be moved from the source page\'s history to the destination page\'s history. If omitted, the entire page history of the source page will be merged into the destination page.\";'),(_binary 'en',_binary 'messages:apihelp-mergehistory-param-to',_binary 's:98:\"Title of the page to which history will be merged. Cannot be used together with <var>$1toid</var>.\";'),(_binary 'en',_binary 'messages:apihelp-mergehistory-param-toid',_binary 's:98:\"Page ID of the page to which history will be merged. Cannot be used together with <var>$1to</var>.\";'),(_binary 'en',_binary 'messages:apihelp-mergehistory-summary',_binary 's:21:\"Merge page histori